dct_title_s: Pan-European oil & gas map / produced by the Petroleum Economist Ltd., London, in association with Dresdner Kleinwort ; [prepared by] Petroleum Economist Cartographic ; designed, produced, and distributed by the Petroleum Economist Ltd. ; designed by P. Bush and K. Fuller.
dct_description_sm: Shows fields, pipelines, processing plants, storage facilities, LNG facilities, tanker terminals, and refineries. Relief and depths shown by gradient tints. Also covers Turkey, Armenia, Azerbaijan, Georgia and the former Soviet Central Asian republics. "Published October 2006." Inset map: Sakhalin Island. Ancillary map: continuation of map Includes notes, statistical tables, graphs, and key to pipelines.
